[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rio Olympics 2016: Harrison defends judo title as Krpalek wins gold

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Kayla Harrison of the United States beat Audrey Tcheumeo of France by ippon to defend her women's -78kg Olympic judo title in Rio.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
